milestones.description: Jimmy Kamande and Ababu's 44-run partnership is KENYA's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 22 between Martin Suji and Ababu
This is the highest match aggregate (516) involving teams West Indies & Kenya in ODIs
Thomas Odoyo has broken the record for most sixes (14) in ODIs for KENYA, going past Otieno's 12
Odumbe has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (35) for KENYA, going past Otieno
